testProjectsList: SELECT test.name AS Test_name, test.method_name AS Test_method, status.name AS Latest_test_result, test.start_time AS Latest_test_start_time, test.end_time AS Latest_test_end_time, MIN(test.end_time - test.start_time) AS Latest_test_duration, project.name AS PROJECT FROM union_reporting.test JOIN status ON status.id = test.status_id JOIN project ON project.id = test.project_id WHERE project.name = %s GROUP BY PROJECT, Test_name ORDER BY Latest_test_start_time DESC
addTestToProject: INSERT INTO test SET id = %d, name='%s', status_id = %d, method_name = '%s', project_id = %d , session_id = %d, start_time = '%t', end_time = '%t', env= '%s' , browser ='%s', author_id = %s
addScreenshot: INSERT INTO attachment (id, test_id, content_type) SELECT %d, %d, %s FROM OPENROWSET (BULK '%s', SINGLE_BLOB) AS image
